data.description: Over a quarter acre corner lot in town, blank and ready for your dream yard or shop or both! The back yard is fully fenced and has an uncovered patio area and two sheds for storage. Inside you have the farmhouse theme throughout  with a split bedroom, open floor plan, 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a family room. The newly remodeled kitchen is stunning with real wood cabinets , barn wood accents, granite counter tops, hexagon tile backsplash, new stainless-steel appliances, farmhouse sink, new flooring, pantry, fixtures, and breakfast bar. All appliances remain, including the microwave, washer, and dryer. In the now dining area, but what would normally be the living room you have a beautiful coffee bar. The home has new interior paint throughout as well as new flooring except in the primary bedroom and bathroom. The guest bathroom has been remodeled with new vanity, tile flooring and toilet. The primary bedroom had new carpet in 2022, a garden tub/shower combo and plenty of linen storage. This is a must see at a great affordable price!
